    {
      "type": "p",
      "property": null,
      "children": "Tic Tac Toe, also known as “Noughts and Crosses,” is a game that needs no introduction. It's as familiar as your childhood memories and as approachable as a blank sheet of paper. In this game, two players take turns marking their symbol ('X' or 'O') on a 3x3 grid. The goal? To be the first to get three of your symbols in a row, horizontally, vertically, or diagonally. Simple, right? But don't let the simplicity fool you - Tic Tac Toe is a game of strategy, tactics, and, above all, fun."
    },
    {
      "type": "br",
      "property": null,
      "children": null
    },
